---

## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Main piece is not ready by launch date | Build 3-day buffer into the production schedule |
| Low initial engagement | Have amplification content ready; do not panic and change message |
| Negative reception or pushback | Prepare thoughtful response talking points in advance |
| Competitor publishes similar content first | Focus on unique angle; reference their piece and differentiate |

